      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"complex\" is one way to put it but it feels like you're avoiding the real question. if the research shows these laws cause disproportionate harm to minority groups, isn't the \"deterrence\" argument basically just an outdated myth? like, is there any actual proof they make places safer or are we just sticking to them because of tradition?",
